{
  "name": "WorkbookConnection",
  "summary": "<p>连接可存储在 ET 工作簿中。工作簿打开时，ET 创建连接的内存副本，称为连接对象。连接对象包含服务器名称和服务器上打开的对象的名称等信息。连接对象也可以选择包含身份验证凭据和/或一个命令，该命令可传递给服务器执行（例如：由 SQL Server 执行的 SELECT 语句）。</p>\n<p>连接的确切形式取决于数据检索的机制。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“test1”的连接的简要说明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Description</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将基于活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接的第一个范围中的字体设置为斜体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ranges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>连接是从 ET 工作簿之外的外部数据源获取数据所需要的一组信息。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Description",
      "summary": "<p>在 <strong>“连接属性”</strong> 对话框中，用户可以编辑连接的名称和/或说明。在该对话框中更改名称和说明只会更改 ET 连接对象中的相应字段。  </p>\n<p>说明的最大长度为 255 个字符。如果用户指定的连接文件的说明长于 255 个字符，则说明会被截断，以满足 255 个字符的限制。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>WorkbookConnection</strong> 对象的简要说明。可读/写 <strong>String</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个连接的简要说明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Description</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接的简要说明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Description</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置工作簿连接对象的名称。可读/写 <strong>String</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作簿上第一个连接的名称，并刷新该连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;WorkbookConnnection_1&quot;</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接的名称为“test1”，则删除该连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>) {\n        connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ODBCConnection",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定的 <strong>WorkbookConnection</strong> 对象的 ODBC 连接详细信息。只读 <strong>ODBCConnection</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一个 ODBC 连接保存为名为“ODCFile”的 ODC 文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCConnection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SaveAs</span>ODC(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\ODCFile.odc&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张查询表的 ODBC 连接的数据连接文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceConnectionFile</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ODBCConnection",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "OLEDBConnection",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定的 <strong>WorkbookConnection</strong> 对象的 OLEDB 连接详细信息。只读 <strong>OLEDBConnection</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿上创建新的工作簿连接，并设置该OLEDB连接的源数据文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connectionString = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;OLEDB;Provider=Microsoft.ACE.OLEDB.12.0;User ID=Admin;Data Source=D:\\\\示例\\\\示例数据.accdb;Mode=Share Deny None;Jet OLEDB:Engine Type=6;Jet OLEDB:Database Locking Mode=0;Jet OLEDB:Global Partial Bulk Ops=2;Jet OLEDB:Global Bulk Transactions=1;Jet OLEDB:Create System Database=False;Jet OLEDB:Encrypt Database=False;Jet OLEDB:Don&#x27;t Copy Locale on Compact=False;Jet OLEDB:Compact Without Replica Repair=False;Jet OLEDB:SFP=False;Jet OLEDB:Support Complex Data=False;Jet OLEDB:Bypass UserInfo Validation=False;Jet OLEDB:Limited DB Caching=False;Jet OLEDB:Bypass ChoiceField Validation=False&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>2(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;connection_1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>, connectionString, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;SELECT * FROM `test1`&quot;</span>, xlCmdSql)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBConnection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceDataFile</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例\\\\示例数据.accdb&quot;</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBConnection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个 OLEDB 连接的命令串。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CommandText</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "OLEDBConnection",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>��回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Ranges",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定的 <strong>WorkbookConnection</strong> 对象的对象区域。只读 <strong>Ranges</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示基于活动工作簿上第一个连接的第一个范围的地址。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ranges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中基于活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接的第一个范围。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ranges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Ranges",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RefreshWithRefreshAll",
      "summary": "<p>如果返回 <strong>True</strong> ，则刷新连接。 如果返回 <strong>False</strong> ，则不刷新连接。 默认值为 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>确定在执行“全部刷新”时是否应刷新连接。 可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“test1”的连接执行“全部刷新”时是否应刷新连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefreshWithRefreshAll</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一个连接的设置为执行“全部刷新”时不刷新连接，并刷新该连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefreshWithRefreshAll</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TextConnection",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextConnection/TextConnection .htm#TextConnection.TextConnection\">TextConnection</a></strong> 对象，该对象包含有关文本文件查询的信息。 此为只读属性。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个文本连接的视觉布局是否从右到左。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFileVisualLayout</span> == xlTextVisualRTL)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上第一张查询表的文本连接的列格式，并设置该连接的TextFilePromptOnRefresh属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textConnection = connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextConnection</span>\n    textConnection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFileParseType</span> = xlFixedWidth\n    textConnection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFilePromptOnRefresh</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "TextConnection",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回工作簿连接类型。只读 <strong>XlConnectionType</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个连接的类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">switch</span> (connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlConnectionTypeODBC</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据库连接的类型为ODBC&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlConnectionTypeOLEDB</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据库连接的类型为OLEDB&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlConnectionTypeTEXT</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据库连接的类型为TEXT&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlConnectionTypeWEB</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据库连接的类型为Web&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">default</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;其它数据库连接类型&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接类型是否为xlConnectionTypeOLEDB。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConnectionTypeOLEDB)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlConnectionType",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "<p>使用此方法可以删除一个外部数据连接。此方法不适用于与其他工作簿之间的链接。  </p>\n<p>删除连接将不会删除正在使用该连接的任何对象。删除连接将不会导致从文件系统中删除任何连接文件。如果编辑任何这些对象以使用另一个连接，则一切都将重新开始工作。</p>\n<p>那些使用已删除链接的对象所表现出的行为就好像无法建立连接一样。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>删除工作簿连接。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作簿上第一个连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表上第一张查询表的连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">QueryTables</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">WorkbookConnection</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Refresh",
      "summary": "<p>如果 <strong>DisplayAlerts</strong> 属性为 <strong>False</strong>，则不显示对话框，<strong>Refresh</strong> 方法将失败，并引发“连接信息无效”异常。  </p>\n<p>刷新连接失败对刷新其他操作没有任何影响。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>刷新工作簿连接。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作簿上第一个连接的名称，并刷新该连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;connnection_1&quot;</span>\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例刷新活动工作簿上名为“test1”的连接。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> connection = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Connections</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>)\n    connection.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
